          content:
            "| Nutrient      | Better Choice | Worse Choice  |\r\n| ------------- | ------------- | ------------- |\r\n| Calories      | 150           | 300           |\r\n| Saturated fat | 1g (5%DV)     | 8g (40%DV)    |\r\n| Sodium        | 140mg (6%DV)  | 700mg (30%DV) |\r\n| Added sugar   | 5g (10%DV)    | 25g (50%DV)   |\r\n| Fiber         | 6g (21%DV)    | 0g (0%DV)     |",
